The Postmaster of Mafdet has received an expedition commission for a complete navigation survey of the Northern Pyramid. The pyramid complex is a significant structure in the region, but its internal layout has never been comprehensively documented in Mafdet's harbor authority reference files. Chart every accessible chamber, passage, and approach within the pyramid and return with a full navigation record.
Your Northern Pyramid survey has been filed with Mafdet's harbor authority expedition archive. The completed record is now the primary navigation reference for crews operating in the pyramid, and the postmaster has noted this as one of the more complete surveys filed with the harbor authority.
